{"id":73,"idInBook":5114,"chapterId":68,"bookId":1,"arabic":"وَحَدَّثَنِي حِبَّانُ، أَخْبَرَنَا عَبْدُ اللَّهِ، أَخْبَرَنَا ابْنُ جُرَيْجٍ، عَنِ ابْنِ شِهَابٍ، عَنْ عُرْوَةَ، أَنَّ عَائِشَةَ، أَنْكَرَتْ ذَلِكَ عَلَى فَاطِمَةَ‏.‏","english":{"narrator":"Narrated 'Urwa:","text":"Aisha disapproved of what Fatima used to say.'"},"hadithNumber":5114,"vol":6,"hadithId":73,"reference":"68:73","meta":{"id":"bukhari","length":7563,"totalChapters":97,"arabic":{"title":"صحيح البخاري","author":"الإمام محمد بن إسماعيل البخاري"},"english":{"title":"Sahih Al Bukhari","author":"Imam Muhammad ibn Ismail al-Bukhari"}},"chapter":{"id":68,"bookId":1,"arabic":"كتاب الطلاق","english":"Divorce","startHadith":5042,"endHadith":5136,"totalHadiths":95},"version":{"name":"bukhari","title":"Sahih Al Bukhari","chapters":97}}